This is for everyone who has smaller bags 💰 but wants to learn #nfts … I’m not sure if #worldofwomen will be a good investment or flip but I do know it’s a wonderful collection and a great discord community and I think y’all in here can learn a lot by going through the process of buying ETH and setting up a MetaMask and buying on OpenSea … might be fun to learn .. ❤️❤️❤️❤️🖼

Link to the project is in my profile ❤️❤️❤️🖼

You think it’s new, a fad, silly … but it’s not … and the behavior of humans And why the long term opportunity is real is based in the fact that we have been pondering this for over a decade. 

Been on … just been waiting for the timing ⏱ to matter to e masses …

We are in the beginning, but this is going to be a fun decade with many ups and downs but web3 is here, please spend 25 hours of learning about the space, it can help many of you get to professional happiness

node.text: Everyone is so frantic, everyone wants it now, everyone is so worried … take a breathe .. you have a lot of time.. 77% of you seeing this are under 35 … you have so much fucking time … those of you under 60 .. you have 25 more quality years … take a breathe … wanting things to fast makes you take short cuts or run out of steam … slow it the fuck down … be productive but patient 💛💛💛💛☀️
